verse.lines:
{lang-eng}O it is wonderful that He should care for me
Enough to die for me!
O it is wonderful, wonderful to me!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I stand all amazed at the love Jesus offers me,
Confused at the grace that so fully He proffers me;
I tremble to know that for me He was crucified,
That for me, a sinner, He suffered, He bled and died.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I marvel that He would descend from His throne divine
To rescue a soul so rebellious and proud as mine;
That He should extend His great love unto such as I,
Sufficient to own, to redeem, and to justify.{/lang-eng}
